Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭帶八接受馮‧布朗號測試時 殘骸課...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八還是TECHNORA的職員呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為辭職信我扣下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.15,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有薪假 申請假期 事假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼來著？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了各種各樣的方式請假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.66,0:00:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能再休息一個月呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.83,0:00:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.73,0:00:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩萬人考試只收18人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.90,0:00:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對落榜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.16,0:00:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 即使落榜了還能回來的 小八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有一手 課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.84,0:00:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭帶八也要實際參加考試才舒暢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的時候不撞牆不回頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.88,0:00:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我年輕的時候也撞得頭破血流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭破血流的結果就是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八最近好像很無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好是不錯的休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.66,0:01:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考場好像是巴布新幾內亞的萊尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.60,0:01:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我蜜月旅行去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小八那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想游泳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海是不錯 吃的就馬馬虎虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是芋頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管前輩他就只吃肉 正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有奢侈的餘裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅費和住宿費應該都不便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.46,0:01:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 前輩說有辭職金啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.33,0:01:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒有辭職金 因為沒辭職啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.10,0:01:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 頭帶八那傢伙生活費怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用存款吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.90,0:01:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 頭帶八應該幾乎沒存款吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他說要買宇宙飛船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正存點小錢也買不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全賭掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彩票賭馬什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有賭球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.95,0:02:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.62,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說也不可能全部用掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也是社會人啊 不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.06,0:02:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬不得已去銀行貸款就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我得去管制課開會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被邀請去宣傳課的宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好忙好忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 田名部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭帶八要是真有麻煩會打電話來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
